reviewText: I watch this all the time and watch other episodes on YouTube.  Since I work iwth a psychologist and all my friends have kids who can't find jobs, I find Dr. Katz to be hilarious.

This has the first appearance of Dom Irrera on Dr. Katz and great comedy from Ray Romano and Emo Phillips.  While the side stories on this tape are not as good as others, the comedy easily makes up for it.
